      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's... that's a really heavy thing to hear. You think people have to make sacrifices? I just feel so guilty every time I ask for help or need something. It feels like if I could just... not be here, they'd finally be able to breathe again and live their own lives without worrying about me constantly. Does that sound selfish to you?",
